			"title": "Spectating",
			"description": "When a new player joins mid-round, the host sends an RPC telling them to be a spectator.\n\nWhen a player reconnects and their character is still alive, they resume playing.\n\nWhen a player reconnects and their character is dead, the host sends the spectate RPC.\n\nSet _currently_spectated_player to null when round ends and call UI.set_spectated_player(-1)",
